test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (3 == 3 and 3 == 3 and 2 == 3)
 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a9871f253c0>([13])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a9871f253c0> = [[1, 13], [1, 13, 1], [13], [13, 1], [1, 13], [1, 13, 1], ...].count
 +  and   3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a9871f253c0>([1, 13])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a9871f253c0> = [[1, 13], [1, 13, 1], [13], [13, 1], [1, 13], [1, 13, 1], ...].count
 +  and   2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a9871f253c0>([13, 1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a9871f253c0> = [[1, 13], [1, 13, 1], [13], [13, 1], [1, 13], [1, 13, 1], ...].count

 +  where 1 = <built-in function prod>([])
